cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.CC, cs.SE, cs.NI 

This paper is primarily focused on distributed data processing and storage paradigms, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses benchmarking suites suitable for big data applications, which is related to Database Systems (cs.DB). The use of containers for automating the deployment of benchmarking tools is related to Software Engineering (cs.SE). The inclusion of cost metrics based on the underlying cloud platform is related to Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) and Cloud Computing (cs.CC).
